(430, 'P. Clay Sherrod', 'ASO - Conway', 'C/2001 RX14', '2002-12-08 08:00:00', '12.1 (*)', '', '1.2''', '07/09/16', '320', '0.31m SCT/ccd....', 'Still exhibits a fine gently curving tail in PA 320 which broadens over about a 3.3'' length in spite of very bright frosty skies; secondary streamers detected in PA 350 and 292', ''),
