(1471, 'P. Clay Sherrod', 'ASO - Conway', 'C/2001 RX14', '2003-01-09 08:00:00', '10.7 (*)', '', '3.1''', '07/09/16', 'curving from 265', '0.31m SCT/ccd....', 'Tail does not appear to have as much arc to it as before and is somewhat shorter (perhaps 4-5'' length ccd); still strongly concentrated coma (*m2=14.7) and quite large; very well defined perimeter', ''),
