(1483, 'P. Clay Sherrod', 'ASO - Conway', 'C/2001 RX14', '2003-01-26 08:00:00', '10.9 (*)', '', '0.44''', '08/09/16', 'fan 260-322', '0.41m SCT/ccd....', 'Streamers measured via densitometry as: (PA & length) 292deg - 4.5''; 303deg - 3.9'' ; 318 - 1.2''....all curving in characteristic pattern; NOTE a possible segment or bright "knot" suspected in inner coma near nucleus (*m2=14.6ccd) in PA 255 deg from primary center, noted on three images', ''),
